sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SAP as sap-mock-api
    participant ING as ingestion-api
    participant K as Apache Kafka
    participant P as event-processor
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Q as query-api

    SAP->>ING: SAP payload + X-Correlation-ID
    ING->>ING: validate and normalize
    ING->>K: canonical envelope keyed by aggregate ID
    K-->>P: event delivered to consumer group
    P->>DB: insert processed_events(event_id)
    alt duplicate event
        DB-->>P: conflict, already processed
        P-->>K: commit offset
    else valid event
        P->>DB: upsert projection tables
        P-->>K: commit offset
    else non-recoverable event
        P->>K: publish to sap.integration.dlq.v1
        P->>DB: record DLQ status when event_id is available
        P-->>K: commit offset
    end
    Q->>DB: read customers/orders/invoices
    DB-->>Q: projections
